title: Daz3d - Mythical Pixie - Genesis3Male.zip
description:
"On a lonely hill in a far away world
where trees grew wild and ivy twirled
a creature lived in a house made of logs
by a peaceful pond that was filled with frogs

His ears long and pointy, with mischievous grin
He wore trousers made from an animal skin
He got up to all sorts of troublesome fun
And loved to play tricks on everyone"

author 3D Universe


Everyone needs some magic in their lives and the Mythical pixie won't disappoint!

This complete character set that includes everything from the character to the accessories, is an excellent add-on for your magical fantasy renders
